{"type": "article", "id": 26298, "title": "橄榄油包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-03T06:50:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130813SIC1vEFXWyN5aVwq.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><a href=\"http://estudioverus.com/\">Estudio Versus</a> 为 Gardeniers 的橄榄油所设计的包装不同于常规的那些可以看到橄榄油的透明玻璃瓶，让人眼前一亮。它白色的瓶身看上去有些纤细，搭配金色的文字带给人一种高端的感觉。若不是瓶身上绘制精美的蔬菜图片，你或许很难将它同橄榄油联系起来。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130811Q5FuwXny20LExGlr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130811NeMiflS1EILZsp2o.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130812vVxiydpn3ufUszPT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130812TE5xBQl13Kw8PfkG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}